Description:
    Creates the involvements for a given event.

Example:
  Add organizer involvements for XO Ruby 2026 Salt Lake City:
    bin/rails g involvements --event xoruby-salt-lake-city-2026 \
      --name "Organizer" --users "Jim Remsik" --organisations "Flagrant"

    This will create:
      data/xoruby/xoruby-salt-lake-city-2026/involvements.yml

  Add multiple volunteer involvements for XO Ruby 2025 Austin:
    bin/rails g involvements --event xoruby-austin-2025 \
      --name "Volunteers" --users "Rick Benavidez" "Michelle Doltzenrod" \
      "Raluca Badoi" "Mando Escamilla

    This will create:
      data/xoruby/xoruby-austin-2025/involvements.yml
